100_UI/Opening/Telop/text01:
สวัสดี, [A] เธอยังจำ <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">โลก</font> ได้อยู่ไหม? 
มันเป็นดาวเคราะห์น้อยๆ ที่เธอได้เคย <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">ทำลาย</font>
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text02:
เธอจำไม่ได้หรอ? กะแล้วเชียว
<material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">เธอนั่นแหละ เป็นคนทำลาย</font>
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text03:
รู้ว่าการทำลายล้าง จะเกิดขึ้นกับโลกในที่สุด…
มนุษยชาติได้จุดไฟ, ถางป่าไม้, พัฒนาอุตสาหกรรม, และเจริญรุ่งเรือง…
ใช้เวลาอธิฐานแด่พระเจ้า และชื่นชมความสุขเล็กๆ น้อยๆ…
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text04: <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">และเธอ! ก็ได้ทำลายมันทั้งหมด</font>
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text05:
แต่ <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">ท่านเทพผู้ยิ่งใหญ่ (คราเอล)</font> ทรงตัดสินใจให้โอกาส 
กับมนุษยชาติ และกับเธอ
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text06: เธอต้องกลับไปยังผืนดิน และเป็นผู้นำของโลก <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">Craftopia</font> ใบนี้, ให้ไปตามทางอันชอบธรรม
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text07:
เธอจะต้องปราบ <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">มังกร</font>, ด้วย <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">อาวุธในตำนาน</font>, และสร้าง <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">อนุสาวรีย์อันยิ่งใหญ่</font> ที่มองเห็นได้จากทุกหนแห่ง
ในขณะนั้น, เธอจะได้พบกับความลับที่ซ่อนอยู่ในโลกใบนี้
100_UI/Opening/Telop/text08: [A], ใน <material="FOT-TsukuMinPr6-H SDF Material_Red">Craftopia</font>, เธอจะต้องเริ่มต้นใหม่อีกครั้ง

100_UI/Setting/Creative/Mana: มานาเริ่มต้น
100_UI/Setting/Creative/Money: ทองเริ่มต้น
100_UI/Setting/Creative/NoDamage: โหมดไม่สามารถถูกทำลาย
100_UI/Setting/Creative/NoDamage/Detail: คุณจะไม่ได้รับความเสียหายหากคุณเปิดใช้งาน
100_UI/Setting/Creative/NoDeath: โหมดไม่ตาย

100_UI/Setting/Creative/NoHunger: โหมดไม่หิว
100_UI/Setting/Creative/NoHunger/Detail: ความพอใจของคุณจะไม่ลดลงหากคุณเปิดใช้งาน

100_UI/Setting/Creative/Skill: จุดทักษะเริ่มต้น

100_UI/Setting/Creative/Tab/Soon: การตั้งค่าที่สะท้อนทันที

100_UI/Setting/DayTime/Sunset: พระอาทิตย์ตกดิน
100_UI/Setting/DayTime/TimeFlows: ไม่มีเวลาคงที่ (แสงแดดจะเปลี่ยนไปตามเวลาที่ผ่านไป)
100_UI/Setting/Detail/AheadCam: มุมกล้องจะเลื่อนเพื่อให้เห็นทางข้างที่อยู่หน้า
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Aim Assist: การควบคุมทิศทางกล้องจะช้าลงเมื่อเล็งใกล้เคียงเป้าหมายแล้ว ยิ่งปรับสูงก็จะยิ่งช้าลง
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Auto Target: ตัวละครจะหันไปทางศัตรูเมื่อโจมตี; แต่การควบคุมทิศทางตัวละครจะให้ความสำคัญมากว่า ฟังค์ชั่นนี้อาจจะไม่ส่งผลต่อการโจมตีในบางครั้ง
100_UI/Setting/Detail/AutoSave: มีความเป็นไปได้ที่เกมจะค้าง, แคช, หรือสูญเสียไอเทมเนื่องจากตัวเกมอยู่ระหว่างพัฒนา เราแนะนำให้เปิดการเซฟอัตโนมัติไว้
100_UI/Setting/Detail/CameraOffset: ระยะห่างระหว่างผู้เล่นและกล้อง
100_UI/Setting/Detail/CameraRecoil: สั่นกล้องตามแรงดีดของปีน ตั้งค่านี้จะไม่ส่งผลต่อแรงดีดของปืน
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Controller_In_deve:
<size=150%><color=red>ATTENTION!! Controller support is still under development!</color></size>
Compatibility with controllers are still under development so there's a chance that you'll be unable to move the player as you like or you'll encounter bugs At this present time, we recommend playing with the keyboard We're planning to improve the game with the coming updates so please hang on
100_UI/Setting/Detail/DropItem: การปรับจำนวนที่ไอเทมที่แสดง เพิ่มขึ้น อาจทำให้ส่งผลต่อประสิทธิภาพของตัวเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/FarClipPlane: ระยะทางที่เกมจะแสดงผล การลดระยะการเรนเดอร์จะเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพตัวเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/FootPrint: เปิดเพื่อแสดงรอยเท้า การปิดอาจเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพของตัวเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/GrassBend: เปิดใช้งานภาพเคลื่อนไหวหญ้า การปิดใช้งานนี้เพิ่มประสิทธิภาพตัวเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/HomeOnly: ตัวเลือกนี้สามารถเปลี่ยนแปลงได้ผ่านหน้าจอหลักเท่านั้น
100_UI/Setting/Detail/LOD Bias: ปรับเปลี่ยนการเรนเดอร์วัตถุในระยะไกล ยิ่งค่าน้อยลง การเรนเดอร์ก็ง่ายขึ้น ดังนั้นจึงช่วยปรับปรุงประสิทธิภาพ

100_UI/Setting/Detail/Mission: จะแสดงภารกิจที่ ขวา-บน ของหน้าจอ
100_UI/Setting/Detail/PeepCam: ป้องกันมุมกล้องมองทะลุตัวละคร
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Physics Limit:
ปิดการคำนวนฟิสิกส์ เมื่อผู้เล่นอยู่ไกลห่างจากสิ่งก่อสร้าง
  *สามารถปรับได้ในหน้านี้เท่านั้น
  *จะไม่ส่งผลกระทบต่อสายพาน
  *ถ้าใช้ "Artificial Monoliths" ที่สามารถคราฟได้ในเกม, สิ่งนี้จะทำให้คำนวนฟิสิกส์โดยรอบ แม้จะไกลจากผู้เล่นแล้วก็ตามแต่
100_UI/Setting/Detail/PostProcessing: เปิดเพื่อประมวลผลภาพก่อนแสดงผล ทำให้ภาพออกมาสวยงาม ปิดเพื่อเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพของเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Rendering accuracy: การปรับความละเอียดของการเร็นเดอร์ 3D หากปรับสูง, ภาพจะออกมาสวย, แต่อาจส่งผลต่อประสิทธิภาพของตัวเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/Shadow: เปิดเพื่อแสดงเงา ปิดเพื่อเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพของเกม
100_UI/Setting/Detail/shit: หากปิดจะหา อุนจิ ได้น้อยลง
100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/CanNotTouch: ความยากของเกมสามารถเปลี่ยนแปลงได้ในระหว่างเกมในโหมดผู้เล่นคนเดียว
100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/Casual: สบายๆ : สำรวจโลกและสนุกกับการใช้ชีวิตในโลกกว้าง
100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/Detail:
※ จะบันทึกแยกกันกับโลก
※ ในโหมดเล่นหลายคน, ระดับความยากของเซิฟเวอร์จะถูกนำไปใช้ในเกม
※ การตั้งค่านี้จะส่งผลต่อพลังชีวิตของศัตรู
※ การตั้งค่านี้จะไม่ส่งผลต่อรางวัลและของที่ดรอป

100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/Hell: นรก : แม้กระทั่ง นรก ก็ไม่สามารถกำจัดคุณได้!!
100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/Normal: เอาชีวิตรอด : ต่อสู้กับเหล่าศัตรู
100_UI/Setting/Difficulty/Pro: ยากมาก : สำหรับผู้ช่ำชอง ผู้ที่แข็งแกร่งเท่านั้นถึงจะมีชีวิตรอด
100_UI/Setting/Discard the configuration: ละทิ้งการตั้งค่า
100_UI/Setting/DropItem: จำนวนไอเทมที่แสดง
100_UI/Setting/EnvironmentSound: สิ่งแวดล้อม
100_UI/Setting/FOV: ความกว้างของมุมมอง (FOV)
100_UI/Setting/FarClipPlane: ระยะการแสดงผล
100_UI/Setting/FootPrint: แสดงรอยเท้า
100_UI/Setting/GlobalIllumination: จำลองแสงสมจริง
100_UI/Setting/GraphicPreset: พรีเซ็ต กราฟิก

100_UI/Setting/GraphicQuality: คุณภาพกราฟิก

100_UI/Setting/IslandLevelNotFixed: ไม่มีระดับเกาะคงที่
100_UI/Setting/LOD Bias: ความละเอียดของวัตถุ (LOD Bias)
100_UI/Setting/Left stick threshold: ขอบเขตจอยสติ๊กซ้าย

100_UI/Setting/LightQuality/High: สูง(คุณภาพสูง)
100_UI/Setting/ManualTakeover: โอนย้ายข้อมูล
100_UI/Setting/MaximumFPS: จำกัดเฟรมเรท
100_UI/Setting/Mission: แสดงภารกิจ
100_UI/Setting/MotionBlur: เบลอการเคลื่อนไหวภาพ
100_UI/Setting/OperationPalette: แสดงการควบคุม
100_UI/Setting/PeepCam: ป้องกันมุมกล้อง

100_UI/Setting/PopupNoSave: ไม่พบข้อมูลที่สามารถโอนย้ายได้
100_UI/Setting/PopupNotice: การตั้งค่ายังไม่ถูกปรับใช้ หากย้อนกลับ, การตั้งค่าที่เปลี่ยนแปลงจะถูกละทิ้ง ต้องการย้อนกลับหรือไม่?

การดำเนินการนี้จะรีเซ็ตการตั้งค่าทั้งหมดบนหน้าปัจจุบันเป็นการตั้งค่าเริ่มต้น
คุณแน่ใจหรือไม่

100_UI/Setting/PopupSaveInherit:
โอนย้ายข้อมูลตัวละครเก่าของ Craftopia แล้ว,

100_UI/Tutorial/Text/Creative/First_01:
Welcome to Creative Mode!
Creative Mode is the special mode that focuses on "making things" and has different gameplays
You usually need to defeat enemies and explore around the world to gather materials to craft items, but you no longer need to have materials when you craft items in Creative Mode!
100_UI/Tutorial/Text/Creative/First_02:
Let's open up "Creative Tab" via the TAB menu
You can craft pickaxes, axes, various workbenches at your will
You can also craft items on workbenches and blacksmiths without any materials
Feel free to craft anything you want, but please note that you cannot take items out of Creative Mode!
100_UI/Tutorial/Text/Creative/First_03:
In Creative Setting, you can set various options such as player level, status, nullifying damage to players or buildings
You can do many things in this mode: devote yourself to build with an infinite amount of resources, practice combat against enemies, and compete with your friends on a race circuit that you build
Your imagination is the only limit Hope you'll enjoy Creative Mode!
100_UI/Tutorial/Text/First_01:
ยินตีต้อนรับสูโลกของ Craftopia!
อารยธรรมนั้นถูกทำลายจากการกระทำของคุณ!
เริ่มสร้างอารยธรรมในดินแดนใหม่และฟื้นฟูมวลมนุษย์!
100_UI/Tutorial/Text/First_02:
ในดินแดน Craftopia, สามารถเก็บเกี่ยวทรัพยากรตามพื้น
สำรวจพื้นที่, ขุดแร่, และสร้างไอเทมอำนวยความสะดวกในการผจญภัย!
100_UI/Tutorial/Text/First_03:
จำนวนการสร้างสิ่งของจะเพิ่มขึ้น เมื่อซ่อมแซม "หอคอย" และการเปลี่ยน "ยุคสมัย"!
ทำภารกิจและอัพเกรด ยุคสมัย เพื่อการสร้างสิ่งของที่ดีและมีประโยชน์มากขึ้น!

100_UI/VisualTutorial/Anubis/Title: ผู้รับใช้ของพระเจ้า "อนูบิส"
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Anubis1:
อนูบิส เป็นผู้รับใช้ของเทพเจ้า คราเอล ผู้ซึ่งเฝ้าดูโลกแห่งคราฟโทเปีย

อนูบิส จะอวยพรให้คุณโดยแลกกับแผ่นศิลาและลูกแก้ว ไม่แนะนำให้ดูหมิ่นอย่างยิ่ง
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Bed/Title: เตียงนอนและจุดเกิด
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Bed1:
เตียงนอน สามารถใช้ในการกำหนดจุดเกิดใหม่ให้กับคุณได้

โปรดทราบว่าคุณสามารถตั้งค่าจุดเกิดใหม่ได้เพียงจุดเดียวเท่านั้น
100_UI/VisualTutorial/BossRush1:
Boss Rush Dungeon is a difficult dungeon where you face a true challenge
Unlike normal dungeons, you will be forced to battle multiple bosses or risk being surrounded
If you don't have the right equipment or preparation, and not enough confidence in your skills, now is the time to turn back
100_UI/VisualTutorial/BossRush2:
Since the enemies on each floor are randomly selected, the enemies that appear will change each time
In addition, as the floor progresses, the enemy's ability value will gradually increase without an upper limit
Even if the same enemy appears, it will be much stronger than when you fought on the previous floor
100_UI/VisualTutorial/BossRush3:
By choosing to pause at the altar, you can obtain a disc with your progress recorded
If you have a disc, you can resume from the same progress at a later time
In addition, Boss Rush Dungeon does not drop any items other than the exclusive rewards, so concentrate fighting the enemy in front of you!
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Challenge/Title: บททดสอบของ อนูบิส
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Challenge1:
บททดสอบของ อนูบิส สามารถกดท้าทายได้ หากพบเจอในพื่นที่ต่างๆ

บททดสอบของ อนูบิส เนื้อหาในการท้าทายจะแตกต่างกันไป และบางบททดสอบคุณจะต้องมีสิ่งของเฉพาะเพื่อเคลียร์ จะได้รับรางวัลเป็น หินชนวนแห่งการเติบโต เงิน หรือ ค่าประสบการณ์ เมื่อเคลียร์ได้
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Crystal:
Once the stored energy of your weapon is full, "Extractor Paracelsus" can extract an "Energy Crystal" from the weapon

"Energy Crystal" is the crystal that holds the power of defeated monsters
By consuming these crystals, you will obtain a scroll of rare enchantments
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Enchant/Title: ไอเทม เอนชานท์
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Enchant1:
"Enchantment" is the special power that various items have
If you extract its power from items, it'll be "Enchanting Fragment" You can use it apply its enchantment to other items

Enchanting Fragment can be extracted by multi-selecting enchanted items via sub menu of the inventory If you scrollify those fragments, you can give it to other players
100_UI/VisualTutorial/EnchantTable/Title: โต๊ะเอนชานท์
100_UI/VisualTutorial/EnchantTable1:
"Enchanting Table" is the building that you use to consume "Enchanting Fragment" and apply enchantments to items of your choice


Quality and quantity of the enchantments that you can apply to an item is limited by the cost; however, the further era you progress, the higher the cost limit will be
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Farm1:
You can sow seeds onto "Farming Plot" to grow crops

Sowing seeds onto "Farming Plot" and watering them to grow crops
Under special weathers such as "Rainy", Farming Plots will be watered automatically
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Food:
If your "Satiety" is getting low, your maximum "Stamina" will decrease and you will take hunger damage over time

You can consume food items, such as "Animal Flesh" or "Meals" to restore your "Satiety"
You should eat constantly to maintain your "Satiety" in order to survive
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Food/Title: อาหารและความอิ่ม
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack/Title: การโจมตีและชีลด์เบรก
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack1:
บางศัตรูมี "เกจโล่"

ที่จะทำให้ดาเมจจากการถูกโจมตีลดลง เมื่อเกจโลของศัตรูเหลือ 0 ศัตรูจะเกิดการ "ชีลด์เบรก" และจะได้รับความเสียจากการถูกโจมตีมากขึ้น 
บางการโจมตีสามารถเจาะเกราะได้เช่นกัน
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack2:
คุณสามารถ "หลบสมบูรณ์" ได้โดยการ หลบ การโจมตีของศัตรูในเสี้ยววินาที 

 ถ้าคุณทำ "หลบสมบูรณ์" ได้ คุณจะอยู่ในโหมดสโลว์โมชั่นในชั่วขณะและยังสามารถใช้ท่า "โจมตี" เพื่อลด "เกจโล่" ของศัตรูได้ค่อนข้างเยอะ
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack2HSword/: การโจมตีด้วยดาบใหญ่
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack2HSword1:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Two-handed Sword's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will approach an enemy and consume all "Charged" buff to perform vertical slash The more the buff consumed, the more damage it deals
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttack2HSword2: With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will approach an enemy and perform horizontal slash This grants you "Charged" buff for a longer duration than usual
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackBow/Titl: การโจมตีด้วยธนู
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackBow1:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Bow's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will backstep and shoot an arrow at an enemy For a certain duration, the body part which is shot will receive increased damage from arrow and bullet shot by the player who performs the Power Attack
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackBow2: With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will backstep and shoot arrows in a fan shape You can hit multiple enemies with this Power Attack
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackDual/Tit: การโจมตีด้วยดาบคู่
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackDual1:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Dual Wield's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will approach an enemy and perform spin slash which hits an enemy multiple times
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackDual2: With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will approch an enemy and perform consecutive attack that deals AoE damage to a larger area You can only perform this while you have the maximum amount of "Rush" buff
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackGun/Titl: การโจมตีด้วยปืน
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackGun1:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Gun's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will backstep to maintain proper distance and shoot all bullets remaining in a magazine If no bullets remain in a magazine, this Power Attack reloads instead
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackGun2: With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will backstep to maintain proper distance and throw an Explosive Barrel to make it explode If no bullets remain in a magazine, this Power Attack reloads instead
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackKatana/T: การโจมตีด้วยดาบคาตานะ
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackKatana1: Katana's Power Attack can be performed with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM] after successful "Perfect Dodge" or counterattacks
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackKatana2:
1 After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Katana's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will approach an enemy and perform horizontal slash to deal damage to surrounding If Detect buff has 4 or more stacks, this Power Attack consumes 3 stacks to perform thrust attack as well If Detect buff has the maximum stack, this Power Attack performs additional attack
With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will approach an enemy and perform horizontal slash to deal damage to surrounding
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackKatana3:
2 There are 2 types of counterattack, "Returning Stance" counterattack and "Detect" counterattack
　You can perform "Returning Stance" counterattack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM] at the moment of an enemy's attack
　With [KEYMAP:MELEE], "Returning Stance" counterattack has a shield bash effect, and the motion of the following Iai attack will be greatly changed
　With [KEYMAP:AIM], "Returning Stance" counterattack has a shield bash effect, and it deals AoE shield breaking damage to a large surrounding area

　You can perform "Detect" counterattack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM] at the moment of an enemy's attack while returning Katana into the sheath
　With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will approach an enemy and perform horizontal slash to deal damage to surrounding If Detect buff has 4 or more stacks, this Power Attack consumes 3 stacks to perform thrust attack as well If Detect buff has the maximum stack, this Power Attack performs additional attack
　With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will approach an enemy and perform horizontal slash to deal damage to surrounding
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackLance:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Spear's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE]

You will approach an enemy and perform vertical slash If you throw a spear before the Power Attack, you will retrieve the spear This Power Attack grants you "Throw Spear" buff
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackLance/Ti: การโจมตีด้วยหอก
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackShield:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Shield's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:AIM]

You will approach an enemy and deal AoE damage to a surrounding area
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackShield/T: การโจมตีด้วยโล่
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackStaff/Ti: การโจมตีด้วยคฑาเวทมนต์
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackStaff1:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform Magic Staff's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE] or [KEYMAP:AIM]

With [KEYMAP:MELEE], you will absorb energy from an enemy This Power Attack grants you "Concentration" buff
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackStaff2: With [KEYMAP:AIM], you will backstep and shoot multiple Arcane Bolt
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackSword:
After successful Perfect Dodge, you can perform One-handed Sword's Power Attack with [KEYMAP:MELEE]

You will approach an enemy and perform melee attack
100_UI/VisualTutorial/JustAttackSword/Ti: การโจมตีด้วยดาบ
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Mission1:
In the "Mission" screen, you can check the detail of ongoing quests

If you forget what to do in a quest, please open the "Mission" screen
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Portal/Title: ประตูวาร์ป
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Portal1:
ประตูวาร์ป เป็นสิ่งก่อสร้างที่ทำให้เดินทางได้อย่างรวดเร็ว

ประตูวาร์ป สามารถกดเปิดใช้งานได้ คุณสามารถเดินทางรวดเร็วไปที่ หอคอย ได้เลย
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Prism1:
"มอนสเตอร์ปริซึม" can be used to capture monsters
In order to capture monsters, you need to weaken them by decreasing their life first
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Prism2:
"Pet Management Machine" can be used to tame captured monsters as your pet

Your pet will learn skills and join your combat
100_UI/VisualTutorial/QuestRoot1:
If you open the "Map" after accepting "Quest", the positions of required items and target monsters will be displayed on the map

If you forget where to go in a quest, please open the "Map"
100_UI/VisualTutorial/RespawnPoint/Title: ดาบใหญ่แห่งการฟื้นฟู
100_UI/VisualTutorial/RespawnPoint1:
ดาบใหญ่แห่งการฟื้นฟู เป็นสิ่งก่อสร้างที่ทำให้เกิดใหม่ที่นี่ได้เมื่อตาย

ดาบใหญ่แห่งการฟื้นฟู สามารถกดเปิดใช้งานได้ และคุณสามารถเกิดใหม่ที่ดาบใหญ่แห่งการฟื้นฟู ที่คุณอยู่ใกล้หลังจากตาย สามารถเดินทางรวดเร็วมาที่ดาบใหญ่ได้
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Smelting1:
"Refinery" is the building that you use to strengthen weapons

You can strengthen weapons of your choice by consuming "Refining Stone"
The type of "Refining Stone" required is varied on weapon's level
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Smelting2:
"Refining Scrap Bench" is the building that you can scrap weapons to obtain "Refining Stone"

You can consume "Refining Stone" at "Refinery" to strengthen your weapons
100_UI/VisualTutorial/SoulOrb/Title: ลูกแก้ววิญญาน
100_UI/VisualTutorial/SoulOrb1:
"Soul Orb" is the crystalized soul that is hidden in a variety of place around the world

You can give obtained Soul Orbs to "Anubis" to exchange with special items
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Terminal1:
After you clear a dungeon, you can directly enter the boss fight when you re-enter the dungeon

You can change its setting by interacting with a device next to the gate
You'll be able to challenge the dungeon with higher difficulty by increasing era level
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Torch/Title: กลางคืนและคบเพลิง
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Torch1:
At night, your vision is limited and some enemies start to act violently
"Torch" can be used to light up surroundings and caves

You can equip "Torch" to activate its effect
"Torch" can be crafted on "Workbench"
100_UI/VisualTutorial/Tower1:
หอคอยลิ่ม เป็นสิ่งปลูกสร้างสำคัญที่สามารถซ่อมแซมได้โดยการหาวัสดุ

หลังจากที่คุณซ่อมแซม หอคอยลิ่มแล้ว สิ่งปลูกสร้างที่สำคัญรอบๆหอคอยจะเปิดใช้งาน และสิ่งนี้ทำให้คุณสามารถเทเลพอร์ตไปยังหอคอยอื่นหรือประตูวาร์ปได้ และเพื่อปลดล็อคคุณสมบัติของ ความก้าวหน้าของยุค
100_UI/VisualTutorial/WireHook1:
"Wire Hook" is the equipment that allows you to move swiftly to the direction of your choice

You can continuously use it up to twice, even in a midair, to move or dodge acrobatically
100_UI/WorldCreate/EnterWorldName: ตั้งชื่อโลก

101_Tips/0: เมื่อเลเวลเพิ่มขึ้น คุณจะมีแต้มสกิล, แล้วจึงจะสามารถเรียนสกิลได้
101_Tips/1: เมื่อใช้งาน อาวุธ/เครื่องมือ จะทำการชาร์จ "พลังงานสะสม" เมื่อใดที่เก็บพลังงานจนเต็มจำนวน, คุณจะได้รับ "คริสตัลพลังงาน" ที่สามารถเพิ่มความแรร์เอนชานท์ได้
101_Tips/10: "การกลิ้งหลบ" เป็นทักษะสำคัญในการต่อสู้ หากคุณหลบได้ตรงจังหวะ, คุณจะสามารถสวนกลับด้วย "การโจมตีรุนแรง" ได้
101_Tips/11: "หีบ" สามารถคราฟ แล้วเก็บของใส่ข้างในได้
101_Tips/12: จะใช้งานดาบสองมือหรือคาตานะได้, ต้องเรียนสกิล "ทักษะดาบสองมือ" ก่อน
101_Tips/13: เมื่อสวมใส่เครื่องร่อน, กดปุ่มกระโดดขณะกระโดดอยู่ เพื่อร่อนเครื่องร่อน
101_Tips/14: หากคุณพึ่งเล่นครั้งแรก ให้ลองตรวจสอบดูบนมุมขวาบนของหน้าจอเพื่อดูภารกิจต่างๆ
101_Tips/15: อยากสร้างอาวุธเพิ่มมั้ย? ขั้นแรก สร้างโต๊ะประดิษฐ์ก่อน หลังจากนั้นสร้างโรงตีเหล็ก
101_Tips/16: สิ่งก่อสร้างและยานพหนะ วางแล้วสามารถถอนคืนเป็นไอเทมได้
101_Tips/17: โมโนเป็นสิ่งมีชีวิตลึกลับที่มีอยู่ในโลกคราฟโทเปียมานานแล้ว มีข่าวลือว่าพวกมันมาจากสุดขอบของจักรวาล หากสาดน้ำใส่พวกเขาจะ?
101_Tips/18:
หากโยน มอนสเตอร์ปริซึม ใส่สิ่งมีชีวิต, คุณสามารถจับมันได้
มนุษย์ก็เช่นกัน เพราะเป็นสิ่งมีชีวิต
101_Tips/19: หากแลกเปลี่ยน "หินชนวนแห่งการเติบโต" กับอนูบิสบนเกาะ, สามารถเพิ่มค่าพลังชีวิต และมานาได้
101_Tips/2: หากต้องการสกิลระดับ 2, จะต้องเรียนสกิลระดับ 1 ให้ครบจำนวนก่อน
101_Tips/20: [ITEM:1920] เป็นสิ่งอำนวยความสะดวกที่เก็บไม้ในพื้นที่มากองรวมกันไว้ โดรนไม่สามารถตัดต้นไม้เองได้
101_Tips/21: ต้องการเบ็ดที่ดีกว่านี้หรอ? คราฟ [ITEM:2124] สิ! คุณจะมีโอกาสได้รับปลามากขึ้นต่อการตกหนึ่งครั้ง
101_Tips/22:
"สำหรับผู้เล่นขั้นสูง"
มาเริ่มการผลิตอัตโนมัติกันดีกว่า เริ่มจากวางเครื่องขุดแร่ที่แท่นหิน จากนั้นวาง รางเลื่อน ลากแร่ไปยังฐาน
101_Tips/23:
"สำหรับผู้เล่นขั้นสูง"
ด้วยประโยชน์ของ "โต๊ะขัดอาวุธ", สามารถทำให้อาวุธแข็งแกร่งขึ้นได้
โดยการใช้ "หินขัดอาวุธ" เพื่อเสริมแกร่งให้อาวุธได้ที่ "โต๊ะขัดอาวุธ"
101_Tips/24:
หากติดตั้งเครื่องดูดไว้ที่หีบ,
มันจะดูดของที่อยู่รอบๆ เข้าในหีบเก็บของ
101_Tips/25:
"สำหรับผู้เล่นขั้นสูง"
ติดตั้ง [ITEM:1926] ไว้ที่หีบแล้วชี้ไปที่เครื่องคราฟ; มันจะส่งไอเทมเข้าไปคราฟของเอง
หากติด [ITEM:1924] กับเครื่องคราฟด้วย, ก็จะกลายเป็นผลิตภัณฑ์ที่ผลิตอัตโนมัติ
101_Tips/26: เมื่อจะไปสำรวจในพื้นที่ที่มีความร้อนสูง แนะนำให้คราฟ [ITEM:5546] แล้วติดมือไปด้วยจะดีมาก
101_Tips/27: สำเร็จทุกภารกิจใน หมวดหมู่ภารกิจ จะได้โบนัสด้วย เช่น เพิ่มช่องกระเป๋าหรือแต้มสกิลเพิ่มเติม
101_Tips/28:
บางไอเทมบนโลกนี้จะมี "เอนชานท์" ด้วย เช่น "[ENCHANT:54]" and "[ENCHANT:11]" 
ยิ่งเอนชานท์ที่ดีกว่า, ยิ่งเพิ่มค่าพลังได้มากกว่า
101_Tips/29:
"สำหรับผู้เล่นขั้นสูง"
สามารถสกัด "เอนชานท์" จากไอเทมเป็นชินส่วนได้, ไว้ใช้กับ "โต๊ะเอนชานท์" เพื่อเลือกเอนชานท์ได้
ยิ่งอัพเกรดยุคสมัย, ก็จะยิ่งเอนชานท์ได้มากขึ้น!
101_Tips/3: รับค่าประสบการณ์จากการกำจัดศัตรู เมื่อเพียงพอต่อการขึ้นเลเวล ก็จะได้รับแต้มสกิลจากการขึ้นเลเวล
101_Tips/30: คราฟ [ITEM:206] หากต้องการตกแต่งฐานของคุณ ไอเทมที่มีประโยชน์อย่างเช่น [ITEM:5141], เพื่อป้องกันไม่ให้สิ่งมีชีวิตเกิดในบริเวณใกล้เคียง
101_Tips/31:
สามารถคราฟยานพหนะได้ที่ โรงงานเครื่องจักร
สามารถใช้มันในการเดินทางไปรอบๆ ได้
101_Tips/32: สิ่งก่อสร้างที่ทำด้วยไม้เป็นวัตถุไวไฟ มีคนรายงานมาว่า: บ้านทั้งหลังโดนเผาไฟจากวัวป่าที่เดินไปโดนกองไฟ ฉนั้นระวังกันด้วย
101_Tips/33: สู้กับมอนสเตอร์มันยาก? งั้นเรียน [ITEM:859] ลากใส่ปุ่มลัดและลองเอาไปใช้ดูสิ มันจะช่วยได้อย่างแน่นนอน
101_Tips/34: สามารถผสมพันธุ์สัตว์ได้ด้วยการ นำสัตว์สองตัวเข้า [ITEM:293]
101_Tips/35: [ITEM:3516] สามารถคราฟได้ แล้วนำมอนสเตอร์ที่จับมาทำให้มันเชื่องเป็น "สัตว์เลี้ยง" ได้
101_Tips/36:
คุณไม่สามารถจับบอสได้ด้วย มอนสเตอร์ปริซึม!
เพื่อที่จะจับ, คุณควรทำให้พวกมันอ่อนแอลงและโจมตีพวกมันด้วย [ITEM:3515] 4 อันเพื่อกักตัวไว้ก่อนโยน มอนสเตอร์ปริซึม!
*โปรดทราบว่าขณะนี้ไม่มีบอสทุกตัวที่จะจับได้
101_Tips/37: สามารถทำให้มอนสเตอร์เชื่องด้วย [ITEM:3516] แล้วก็ขี่มันซะ, ออกไปสำรวจด้วยกัน, และต่อสู้ด้วยกัน
101_Tips/4: บางครั้งการเล่นหลายคนอาจไม่สเถียร หากมีบางอย่างผิดปกติ แก้ปัญหาเฉพาะหน้าได้ด้วยการรีสตาร์ทเกม
101_Tips/5: คุณสามารถโจมตีหรือขุดได้ด้วยการคลิกค้างไว้ หากคุณเบื่อหรือเมื่อยกับการคลิกซ้ำๆ ให้ใช้การคลิกแบบค้าง
101_Tips/6: เครื่องมือเช่นถัง (น้ำ) หรือเมล็ดพันธุ์สามารถวางเป็นอาวุธย่อยทางขวามือและสามารถใช้งานได้โดยการคลิกขวา
101_Tips/7: ด้วยการลงทะเบียนรายการเข้ากับปุ่มลัดที่ด้านล่างของหน้าจอ คุณจะสามารถใช้รายการได้โดยไม่ต้องเปิดหน้าจอเมนู
101_Tips/8: อาวุธและชุดเกราะสามารถวางบนปุ่มลัดได้
101_Tips/9:
คุณสามารถใช้ถัง(เปล่า) และใช้รอบๆ แหล่งน้ำ เพื่อรับถัง(น้ำ)
ด้วยการใช้ถัง(น้ำ) บนทุ่งข้าวสาลีหรือแปลงเกษตรกรรม คุณสามารถเริ่มผลิตได้

203_ItemDescription/3215: Facility for repairing your equipment's maximum durability It seems as if equipments with less than satisfactory maintenance always break when you need them the most To avoid this, you should always keep your equipments in good shape, but is it still the same item even if you've repeatedly replaced parts of them?
203_ItemDescription/3216: A higher-level repair station can repair items faster The skilled workers seem to prefer the difficult-to-handle vertical cutting machines and shaping machines to the current mainstream milling machines By looking at the belt-type power transmission system connected to the void, it may not be easy to distinguish between magic and science
203_ItemDescription/3227: You can store your money safely in this facility A deposit equal to the amount of money handled is required for approval to establish the facility, and a 1% fee is charged for withdrawals The more you place, the more you can store It may be a more shady business than a store that demands a huge appraisal fee and then sells it the next day at double the price
203_ItemDescription/3228: When placed, the bank's maximum deposit amount will be increased by 20 million Gs If the bank is not installed, there is no effect
203_ItemDescription/3239: This pochette contains tools that assist you in combat Just because there are more tools than you expected doesn't mean it's connected to the fourth dimension, and losing it doesn't mean the adventure begins
203_ItemDescription/3240: This pochette contains tools that assist you in combat The small bottle covered in the practical items holds the record of the bitter youth full of regrets It's been a long time waiting for the miracle to happen somewhere, someday
203_ItemDescription/3241: A bar-shaped grinding stone made of hard steel It quickly and messily scrapes off the oil and rust from the blade and revives its sharpness If you want to keep cutting your enemies efficiently, you may want to imitate the traditional style of holding a knife in your right hand and a sharpening stick in your left
203_ItemDescription/3242: An iron plate soaked with numerous grudges Kneeling is a ritual that is performed by selected people who know pride and shame to apologize only once in their lives The strength of one's will to keep one's head up, even on a burning iron plate, is of great magical significance
203_ItemDescription/3243: This special amulet seems to be effective only when you equip two-handed swords
203_ItemDescription/3244: This special amulet seems to be effective only when you equip two-handed swords
203_ItemDescription/3290: A practice shell It's not very powerful, and it doesn't give a numbing sensation when fired, so it's not well received by gunners who only need one shot Equip this to fire when riding a tank
203_ItemDescription/3291: A shell for attacking a wide area You can aim it directly, though; it's fun to aim it indirectly, then guide the enemies into the firing range to hit them Equip this to fire when riding a tank
203_ItemDescription/3292: This shell is designed to pierce through thick armor Colossal monsters and dragons are no exception Equip this to fire when riding a tank
203_ItemDescription/3300: A worn out holy sword The original sword is a sword that holds the power of the stars, but this is an original-like replica It still glows because of the mystical power of the original, but it will soon be empty, leaving no trace of it behind
203_ItemDescription/3301: A worn out magic sword It once used to be a strangely twisted sword, but now there is no trace of its unique features It still glows because of the mystical power of the original, but it will soon be empty, leaving no trace of it behind
203_ItemDescription/3302: A worn out demonic sword It was originally an inseparable twin sword, but now only one half remains It still glows because of the mystical power of the original, but it will soon be empty, leaving no trace of it behind
203_ItemDescription/3303: A worn out katana It was originally a katana with a very long blade, but now it is broken and shortened It still glows because of the mystical power of the original, but it will soon be empty, leaving no trace of it behind

203_ItemDescription/3331: This beautiful petal can remind some of the romantic storms of old times, the island that never withers, or youthful days in school life
203_ItemDescription/3332: These colored fallen leaves can make you feel a sense of burning beauty and gentle harvest Let's take a share of the harvest from nature without making the god of harvest angry
203_ItemDescription/3333: These colored fallen leaves make you feel a sense of beauty and loneliness at the same time The gods have fallen in love with the magnificent beauty of nature No words can't describe it
203_ItemDescription/3334: Hydra's reversed scales are valuable Even obedient dragons will kill human beings when they touch their reversed scales It is easier to collect Hydra's reversed scales since they have more heads than other dragons
203_ItemDescription/3335: This reversed scale is taken from the enraged Hydra that has been addicted to poison Human monarchs also have their reversed scales, so avoiding them is the key to a successful life

203_ItemDescription/3352: Rare material which can be used to craft equipment
203_ItemDescription/3353: Dragon scales are rare materials for crafting equipment Their lightweight and hardness can be used to produce fine weapons and armors Moreover, since dragons are enormous creatures, once they are defeated, factories and villages will be built to gather, process, and sell their materials This will revitalize logistics and provide job opportunities for delivery persons In other words, defeating dragons is an effective measure against unemployment
203_ItemDescription/3354: Executioner scales are rare materials for crafting equipment Only the elite and honored can have these scales Their strength is very high due to their usual condition of healths They probably consumed a well-balanced diet of vegetables and insects, avoiding mealworms because of their high-fat content, and never missed a dusting when eating crickets
203_ItemDescription/3355: These scales are rarely dropped by reapers Reapers often have their roots in the deep sea, so scales inherited from their ancestors may grow in hidden parts If you touch their scales, you may be forced to marry them
203_ItemDescription/3356: This is a small fragment of a meteorite that very rarely falls from the sky It can be used to craft rare items
203_ItemDescription/3357: This is a fragment of a meteorite that very rarely falls from the sky It can be used to craft rare items
203_ItemDescription/3358: This is a large fragment of a meteorite that very rarely falls from the sky It can be used to craft rare items
203_ItemDescription/3360: This red vegetable grows in hell The one planted by demons, grown in disgust, harvested by evil men, is said to be the spiciest of all This is one of the essential ingredients for hell-flavored potions You'd better behave as the devil does in hell if you'd like to have this
203_ItemDescription/3361: This stone is always faintly warm It does not generate heat but blocks heat You can use this behavior to craft heat-resistant equipment, but the heat blocking behavior is the hobby of the fairies; you must check the resistance carefully when using it, or they will betray you

203_ItemDescription/3367: The cooling of viscous magma forms this rock There are traces of magma flowing through the ground, and volcanologists or geologists can determine the origin and crystal structure The technique of tearing the whole area to pieces with an iron ball is named after this rock
203_ItemDescription/3368: This rock is one of the olivines sometimes produced from the ground when the lava erupts It's also treated as a gemstone and looks good on a sexy team
203_ItemDescription/3369: This extraordinary stone found near a lava tube has the Widmanstätten structure With all of the objective data, we can conclude that it can only be obtained after a million years of cooling, not from lava, but from beyond the sky

203_ItemDescription/3371: This is a chunk of snow If someone is rolling snow, I will help them roll it and leave when it's done I want to be that kind of adult
203_ItemDescription/3372: This is the bone meal of gigantic creatures It can be sintered to make parts that do not wear down or used as a magical power sensor due to its high magical conductivity
203_ItemDescription/3373: This part has a complex structure There are cracks in places, but they seem to heal themselves with proper treatment A cycle of excavation from the mountain has been established
203_ItemDescription/3374: These special parts are made with the technology from the lost generation It seems you can use this when you craft a weapon

203_ItemDescription/3415: A hugely profitable contract made out of charcoal and rags that can be found anywhere Without this contract indicating a special permit, no special building can be built But be careful You are not the one who has obtained permission, but the one who owns the contract Don't play the game; if you lose the bet, the contract will be taken away from you

203_ItemDescription/3800: This large facility can produce crude oil stably You can only deploy onto the point of the ocean that has enough depth for it
203_ItemDescription/3801: A great tombstone A monument so large that it can be spotted from outer space is surely to be remembered as long as humanity persists
203_ItemDescription/3802: Monument made of huge stones A civilization that achieved the ability to freely combine such enormous rocks into these formations are unlikely to be bound by this small planet
203_ItemDescription/3803: A giant temple dedicated to the gods Only the most mature social system could afford the constant offerings and festivals
203_ItemDescription/3804: A house of prayer with history and tradition The ultimate culmination of culture, with the highest form of art and countless days and nights spent, demonstrates its superiority to its surroundings
203_ItemDescription/3805: This world heritage seems to be able to generate Enchantments Points over time and to accumulate up to 10 points However, this effect is not stackable even if you deploy two or more of these buildings on the same island
203_ItemDescription/3840: An orb fulfilled with souls of Anubis Many orbs were spread into various places around the world, but their number is way too smaller than the one of souls you've taken from Anubis
203_ItemDescription/3851: This offering showing the skills dedicated to the gods is required when you progress an Era It seems that a sword and shield made of minerals and bullion for decoration are needed
203_ItemDescription/3852: This offering showing the skills dedicated to the gods is required when you progress an Era It seems that a large amount of bread, meat, and fish are needed
203_ItemDescription/3853: This offering showing the courage dedicated to the gods is required when you progress an Era It seems that relics that lie on the fields of meadow, ice fields, deserts, volcanic mountains, and poisonous swamp biomes are needed
203_ItemDescription/3854: This offering showing the might dedicated to the gods is required when you progress an Era It seems that tokens that can be obtained by defeating a lizard, a dead spirit, a serpent, a flower spirit, and a mono-eyed king at Lv 30 or higher are needed
203_ItemDescription/3856: This offering showing the knowledge dedicated to the gods is required when you progress an Era It seems that you can obtain this by defeating the three-headed dragon living in the poisonous swamp
203_ItemDescription/3861: This relic seems to be left behind by the people who once lived on the meadow It could be an offering to the gods or demanded by some collectors

203_ItemDescription/4001: A stone wall devised by castle lords Even ninjas can't get through it! Strong enough to withstand attacks by land or sea
203_ItemDescription/4002: Wall of a certain hitchhiker's house Laying infront of this wall might be great for avoiding being crushed by a bulldozer Letting a hyperspace highway pass and pressing a red button isn't much of a difference
203_ItemDescription/4003: A single board cut out from Yggdrasil The gigantic tree ring looks as if it is parellel even when cut in round slice It was once a holy tree that ws feared by the angels but now, it is a cheap material thanks to the overflowing mana in this world
203_ItemDescription/4004: A flat board An absolutely flat wooden board Reminds you of someone nevermind Didn't know Bacura was a material for construction If there was any impoliteness in this description, we will apologize flat out
203_ItemDescription/4005: A wall with the same pattern as the ruins of an ancient civilization The geometric pattern on the wall describes a sophisticated ancient technology that is long forgotten
203_ItemDescription/4006: Brick wall built by an artisan It has a mesmerizing geometry, and it is said that you are able to tell various things like the artisan's age or their place of birth just by looking at it
203_ItemDescription/4007: Patchworked wall that has been repatched numerous times Due to the space debris creating a hole on the body of the ship in space, it is heavily repatched Here, the humans are the cause of the hole In other words, the humans are the debris
203_ItemDescription/4008: A wall with the same pattern as the ruins of an ancient civilization The geometric pattern on the wall describes a sophisticated ancient technology that is long forgotten
203_ItemDescription/4020: This wall makes you want to scribble on it It has stimulated the creative urge of every artist and preserved all kinds of works by various artists These walls have remained the same, even after the red button The masterpieces are called frescoes
203_ItemDescription/4021: This wall is made of boiling lava pressed into a plate by an unknown force Players will take damage in contact with this, but other mobs and materials will not be damaged due to the safety measures What is safety?
203_ItemDescription/4022: You can color this wall by using the item "Spray Paint" The reason why you cannot make the artistic graphics over the walls is you are following the local government rules
203_ItemDescription/404: This campfire is one of the basic tools of adventurers It's recommended to cook meat over the fire since you will receive damage when you consume raw meat You can ride the updraft arising from a campfire with a glider to fly efficiently
203_ItemDescription/4101: A floor that is cool in summer but cold in winter It's useful in hot climates but you may want to lay a carpet on top in colder climates
203_ItemDescription/4102: A floor of a man working at his local radio station This floor is located at a "harmless"planet, not found currently but found in the future Lining up some fish would be nice The dophins will surely appreciate it
203_ItemDescription/4103: A single board cut out from Yggdrasil Feared by the angels back when it was still a part of the Yggdrasil, it has let many kinds of heros step past it Now that the manas are overflowing everywhere, it is used as a commodity
203_ItemDescription/4104: A floor layed with lumbered wooden boards The flat board can be used as a cutting board Or maybe, it's made to be a cutting board? The word "cutting board" used here isn't a reference of somebody by the way
203_ItemDescription/4105: The floor of the ruins of an ancient civilization The world destruction program engraved on the surface can only be understood by electronic minds As they are activated by the red button, agents named after fairies guard the button
203_ItemDescription/4106: Floor made of sun-dried bricks In arid regions, manure was used to reinforce their floors and were collected meticulously as they had various usage
203_ItemDescription/4107: A floor that has been repaired numerous times After repairing the hole in the floor everytime  the hole is spotted, it became a patchwork style But the experience of reparing will guide you to a newer technology The world needs bugs for innovation
203_ItemDescription/4108: A light-weighted ceramic floor A very excellent material, but when utilizing the topology optimization to the crystal structure on it, it causes a hole that will lead you to the science world When you offer a cake to it, it returns as a lie
203_ItemDescription/4117: This floor is planted with a large amount of grass It's been said that "the more grass grows, the heavier it gets" since ancient times, and it seems the traditional phrase can be applied to this floor as well
203_ItemDescription/4121: This floor is made of boiling lava pressed into a plate by an unknown force Players will take damage in contact with this, but other mobs and materials will not be damaged due to the safety measures What is safety?
203_ItemDescription/4122: You can color this floor by using the item "Spray Paint" This floor seems to be affected by a special skill, so you can apply color evenly without applying primer beforehand
203_ItemDescription/416: This will allow you to age food materials and some items to mature You can create some potions with this too Contamination? I've never heard of it
203_ItemDescription/4201: A tilted stone wall devised by castle lords Tilted at an angle to prevent samurai from scaling it It can even keep ninjas out!
203_ItemDescription/4202: The slanted wall of a wild man's house in a gown If it starts to fall apart, take only a towel with you If you know where your towel is, you don't really need anything else
203_ItemDescription/4203: A single board cut out from Yggdrasil In this mana-filled world, a legendary sword born from this tree is now mass producable But please, don't thrust the sword to try to re-experience its legacy of the past
203_ItemDescription/4204: A slope affixed with lumbered wooden boards According to the research of a wild Architecture Department of Craftopia student, it is extremely difficult to connect the starting point to the end point using all of the slope series If you can connect it perfectly without missing, you're on your way to get a Bachelor's Degree
203_ItemDescription/4205: Walls that withstood years of wind and snow In another universe, a competition where competitors had to cling on the slopes without falling became popular Cheaters were not welcome
203_ItemDescription/4206: Brick slope developed by a distinguished researcher through numerous experiments and calculation Brick walls built diagonally should collapse, logically, but somehow stands as is exceeding the researcher's expectations
203_ItemDescription/4207: A slanted wall coated with zinc steel After the war that destroyed the influstructures, the humans, which lost its ways of creating new materials, restored it using only what they had in hand Let's hope that someday, the memory core with all the information about technology will get discovered
203_ItemDescription/4208: A light-weighted ceramic floor that's a bit worn out This floor has been stepped by many famous spacemen in countless number of  world's timeline James, Jean, Benjamin, Catherine, Johnathan, Michael The super famous 117th John must have stepped on this floor too
203_ItemDescription/4221: This slope is made of boiling lava pressed into a plate by an unknown force Players will take damage in contact with this, but other mobs and materials will not be damaged due to the safety measures What is safety?
203_ItemDescription/4222: You can color this slope by using the item "Spray Paint" This slope seems to be crafted with future technology that does not allow the painting to drip down even when the slope is slanted
203_ItemDescription/428: You can refine your weapons with Refining Stones to increase their ATK Thanks to the update, this can be automated too!
203_ItemDescription/429: You can refine your weapons with Refining Stones to increase their ATK It can probably refine other items too, in the future
203_ItemDescription/4301: One side of a gable wall for the roof A gable wall is a wall which supports the roof You will see this in East Asian hip-and-gable style roof It has a very nice flow of air, works as a chimney that lets the smoke from the hearth out But, the cold wind from the outside is a bit of a downside
203_ItemDescription/4302: One side of a gable wall A weak point against a strung gust A gust strong enough can blow away the roof If calculated right, you might be able to make a flying house
203_ItemDescription/4303: A gable wall for the roof The gaps arn't there for staring at strangers outside The gaps arn't there for being stared at by a stranger outside also
203_ItemDescription/4304: One side of a gable wall for the roof Sorry for the wait We may have made you wait for a bit too long in fact Now this time, you will no longer get frusterated by the cold wind flowing into your room through the cracks
203_ItemDescription/4305: One side of a gable wall A gable wall is a wall which supports the roof
203_ItemDescription/4306: A gable wall for the roof Love filling up the gaps? Well, you will love it even more-- oh, don't mention about the variations It will eventually increase, you will stick around with us for a bit longer  right?
203_ItemDescription/432: This will scrap weapons put into this and generate Refining Stones of the same rank as the weapon Please be alert to your surroundings and don't get yourself into it
203_ItemDescription/44: A one-handed sword made of stone It's better than fighting with your bare hands, but you'll need a stronger weapon if you plan on going into a dungeon
203_ItemDescription/4401: Windows are a framework which connect one universe with another Based on a legend of a goddess slaying a devil through the window with her bow and arrows, the windows in this world are made in a certain size that allows you to snipe enemies through them
203_ItemDescription/4422: You can color this window by using the item "Spray Paint" If the true Craftopian craftsman works on it, they can neatly paint the specified area without masking
203_ItemDescription/45: A one-handed sword made of copper Copper is quite weak, but it's easy to obtain and craft with it It's actually rather precious
203_ItemDescription/4501: Door frames made for you to attach a door to a wall Made with easy setup in mind Daijoubu, here we go!
203_ItemDescription/4509: Wooden arch This is a wooden arch This is no doubt a wooden arch What? Did you just say it doesn't look like one? Citizen, that is considered treason (ZAP!ZAP!) Maybe the next one to press the button will know better
203_ItemDescription/4522: You can color this door frame by using the item "Spray Paint" The reason why this door frame doesn't have a door is that the door will get stuck and will not open if you color the door and the frame at the same time
203_ItemDescription/46: A one-handed iron sword Iron and steel are different so be careful
203_ItemDescription/4601: A straw‐thatched Roof To all piggies, do not take refuge in here The wolves will blow it away To all Wolves, do not blow the roof away You will be stewed and eaten
203_ItemDescription/4602: A roof made from scale-like tiles A fairy-tale-like roof like this give off feelings as if fairies will come visit A fun world like this, citing from the manual, should atleast have 15f
203_ItemDescription/4609: A ceramic roof that's a bit warn out Used as a material for the gigantic spaceship A commander that sits cross-legged and loves to drink some brandy tea might have been here, since the roof's also used for the commander's office A new page of an academic papers being written
203_ItemDescription/464: Autonomously cuts down trees with mysterious force Made with strong focus on safety, so the blades are not dangerous No reports of injury yet, at least
203_ItemDescription/465: Thanks to the technological breakthroughs coming from the company's efforts, you can limit the area and select the target by using Virtual Walls The rotating saws will stop for safety reasons when the owner approaches, so you can collect items from this machine without getting injured
203_ItemDescription/47: A one-handed silver sword Silver is said to fight off evil, and there are monsters that run away just at the sight of it
203_ItemDescription/4701: A flat straw thatched roof It is one of the most attention-gathering material in the Craftopia Plantation Subcommittee In order to have enough supplies of straw, you will need a big supply source, but in this world, that's a little difficult
203_ItemDescription/4702: A roof made of stacking scale-like fragments According to the structural mechanics, this is pointless For the researchers working with the unified field theory might find it interesting Maybe I don't even know
203_ItemDescription/4705: An inorganic-ish roof Imagine being enclosed into a room made out of the material used for this roof, now that's real scary stuff There might be an exit Might have a better luck if you know algebra Same things can be said about life too
203_ItemDescription/473: This reaping machine will reap the surrounding crops at regular intervals once installed It seems to be a common thing in every age that the ancient reliable methods are more appreciated than the noble modern technologies of the future
203_ItemDescription/476: Autonomously mines minerals with mysterious force Only for bedrocks Requires modules for complete automation
203_ItemDescription/48: A one-handed gold sword A sparkling sword for the wealthiest adventurers It sparkles so much that it attracts those who are desperate for riches
203_ItemDescription/480: If you put items into this machine, this will generate and produce recycled materials every time the total price of items reaches a certain amount This machine is designed to reduce the waste of excess items produced by excessive automation
203_ItemDescription/4801: A part useful for filling the little gaps between slopes Perfect to fill that hole in your heart
203_ItemDescription/49: A one-handed platinum sword Why would you use such a precious material to make a sword?
203_ItemDescription/4901: One side of a corner of a roof People laughing at the straws not knowing it's our resident and it supports the walls! It can float without them walls nor them pillars! How's that power of the straws, just look at em go!
203_ItemDescription/4902: One side of a corner of a roof The pillars are no longer with us it is dead But the rafters! The building! It's being supported by a magical power! Even if the surface is covered in molds, just change it up with them brand new straws! Champion of the World Heritage! How's that power of the straws, just look at em go!
203_ItemDescription/4903: A corner of a roof Back when the Building Standards Act was still in effect, you would have had to sign paperworks, turn it in, get rejected, questioned, signed paperworks gets lost, gets found, discussed carefully at the public hearing, gets lost again in this world, no need for that
203_ItemDescription/50: A one-handed sword made of adamantite Rarity doesn't mean destructibility
203_ItemDescription/500: You can use this facility to sell unwanted items on the market Selling items will take a long time, so it is important to act early Generally, higher quality items sell for more
203_ItemDescription/5001: A table with a light color the lifts the spirits Eating with company is very fun If everybody could set aside their differences and sit at the same table and eat, world peace would seem easily achievable
203_ItemDescription/5002: A table with a dark, calming color Eating alone on a big table gives you a strong sense of independence, with no need to worry about others around you If you feel lonely, your smartphone device is a good way to distract yourself Watching a certain twintailed blonde girl struggle at a videogame is pretty great
203_ItemDescription/5003: A large round table Fathers in Japan have long expressed their fatherhood through flipping these tables vertically 540° Over the years, the round tables have increased in size and weight, testing the fathers across the country One could track down to this fact as a reason that the strongest being of the world emerged from this coutnry
203_ItemDescription/5004: A round table A round table was used to allow people to speak regardless of their status, but as time passed people started to assign order of class to the seats either way The great king who devised this may be angry to find this out, but he should be more worried about his new form in a recent interpretation
203_ItemDescription/501: You can use this facility to sell unwanted items on the market You can sell more items at once than normal markets
203_ItemDescription/5021: A wooden chair As a result of questioning about why we become hungry, knowing that fighting, or being kind won't help, we discovered that sitting on a chair helps prevent hunger
203_ItemDescription/5022: A chair that prevents you from getting hungry Used for the Craftopia Academy Extreme Chairing Competition Who will discover the weirdest spot you could sit on? The developers are trembling right now
203_ItemDescription/5023: A simple furniture that seats one A little too small to lounge and relax on, but could work in your favor by helping you focus A nice decor as well Sitting on a stool outside brings out my artistic self I guess I can try painting again
203_ItemDescription/5024: A simple furniture that seats one A little too small to lounge and relax on, but could work in your favor by helping you focus A nice decor as well Sitting on a stool outside brings out my artistic self I guess I can try painting again
203_ItemDescription/5025: A simple furniture that seats one Beware of kung fu fighters when they arm themselves with a chair In the hands of a kung fu master, anything is a weapon, a shield, or a trap
203_ItemDescription/5026: A simple furniture that seats one A little rough on the edges Seems it has been brought home by a Japanese middle schooler after making a chair in class
203_ItemDescription/5027: A seat for those waiting for their turn I may be sitting on the bench now, but you never know the next time You could strategize all you want, but in the end, what makes the difference are the basics So I do 100 push-ups, 100 sit-ups, 100 squats, and 10km running every single day
203_ItemDescription/5028: A handmade bench which you could feel the warmth of the tree it was made from Perfect for relaxing out in the sun However, you could choose to float, sink, or fly using this bench This is what true freedom is like
203_ItemDescription/5029: A bench with a backrest Even a common looking bench like this would look more impressive if you found Anubis sitting in it What, no? Of course it would, he's a god
203_ItemDescription/5030: A bench with a backrest It is hoped to bring a new wind to the extreme chairing contest, but its solid four feet would definitely prove to be challenging
203_ItemDescription/5031: This facility relieves your desperate need The significance of owning this facility in place is undeniable both from a hygienic and cultural point of view It is essential for the efficient recovery of special organic compounds; therefore, many of those who pushed that button have requested this facility
203_ItemDescription/5032: This facility relieves your desperate need When you travel long distances after eating and drinking a lot, the facility seen from a distance may be covered in divine lights
203_ItemDescription/5041: A bookshelf with plenty of room All the bookshelf space excites you with the image of all the books you would fill them with The empty space of the bookshelf is just space waiting to be filled by new books The remaining space may be short lived, but enjoy it while it lasts
203_ItemDescription/5042: A bookshelf with plenty of room The ability to store books both vertically and horizontally proves how roomy it is With this amount of space, maybe I can buy that series with very large books I can't wait to see them lined up
203_ItemDescription/5043: Waist height drawers Seeing various sizes of drawers make you feel like you could store anything
203_ItemDescription/5044: Waist height drawers If you don't need to close the drawers afterwards, the most efficient way to check the contents would be to open from the bottom This is useful information only for burglars and heroes, however
203_ItemDescription/5045: Tall shelves not only for storing but also for decorating Decoration is often necessary for those that invite many to their homes The first step to a luxurious lifestyle is decorating your home with tableware The bright color accentuates dark colored plates
203_ItemDescription/5046: Tall shelves not only for storing but also for decorating The dark color compliments white plates very well It is to gain historic presence as the years pass
203_ItemDescription/5047: A common bar counter With enough of these around, you could almost imagine a bard standing in the middle of the bar
203_ItemDescription/5048: A counter you would see in the wild west You see the bar master polishing his glasses, and a regular is smirking at the corner as he sees you You could bravely order rum, order a thin beer, or perhaps ordering milk could be fun as well
203_ItemDescription/5049: A common bar counter With enough of these, you could form a stage for dancers If you are lucky, you could come across a fortune teller taking care of her dancer sister after she's had one too many drinks
203_ItemDescription/5050: A counter you would see in the wild west On these corners you would often see a man of unknown nature drinking alone He could be your rival, or an assassin watching you closely You could ignore him, or talk to him pretending to pick up a coin you dropped
203_ItemDescription/5051: A table you'd want to place next to your bed This drawer has a curse preventing it to be opened Suitable for storing a notebook you cannot afford anybody else seeing it If somebody tries to forcibly open it, it will go up in flames, ensuring you peace of heart when leaving home
203_ItemDescription/5052: A table you'd want to place next to your bed This drawer cannot be opened even with a thief's key, a magic key, or even an ultimate key
203_ItemDescription/5060: If you deploy this stepping stone, you can spawn on its position when you die or re-enter an island However, the effect of bed takes effect before this item's one when you die The effect cannot be triggered in a dungeon
203_ItemDescription/5061: A base bed you can respawn from if you happen to die Cannot be used in a dungeon Wake up to the voice of the early bird and start your day full-throttle, scarfing down a nutritious salad Grab some run-of-the-mill milk and maybe head to Animal Town today, or do you want to look for a wild alpaca you haven't seen yet? Getting a revenge on that guy who killed me isn't so bad too Everything starts from this bed
203_ItemDescription/5062: A base bed you can respawn from if you happen to dieCannot be used in a dungeon After being falsely accused and ducking through an unstable portal, a fierce dragon, raging sheep, and a giant encircling elephant With a knife of determination in your hand, when you die in a full burst, you'll start again from this bed
203_ItemDescription/5063: You can skip a night by sleeping This doesn't set a respawn point
203_ItemDescription/5081: A tent made with thick fabric and wood Perfect for camping, but beware of wild animals Especially bears, since they are known as very curious and stubborn animals; they will find their way into the tent and help themselves with whatever food they find Not to mention you are no exception to the "food" they find
203_ItemDescription/5087: This parasol is the best option to block the harsh sunlight in midsummer You can have the vacation feeling whenever you place a beach chair along with this parasol She's waiting for you on the beach
203_ItemDescription/5088: This parasol is made for blocking sunlight, not for covering you from rain Even though you are caught in a shower in this world, your precious times will not be taken away
203_ItemDescription/51: A one-handed sword made of the legendary mineral mythril It's not a legendary item, even though it's made of legendary materials
203_ItemDescription/5101: A torch to light the dark Also known as Master Torch Practicing ancient martial art techniques had to be kept on the down low, so training was usually done late in the night As the torches, lighting the darkness for the martial artists, were there to witness it all, they eventually earned the title "master" This does not mean you will get stronger trying to fight the torch
203_ItemDescription/5102: Reinforced torches Makes you think about the progress you've made remembering the times you were still using wooden torches
203_ItemDescription/5103: Fancy lighting for your walls The flame makes you think of campfires
203_ItemDescription/5104: This lantern is decorated with auspicious characters known as inverted happiness and necessary decoration for the Lunar New Year It plays a supporting role in both the mysterious room of a Taoist and the cyberpunk eaves of a street vendor In rare cases, it works well with German tanks
203_ItemDescription/5105: This long red lantern is decorated for good luck It's better to cover the walls, floor, ceiling, and the whole area with these lanterns instead of hanging one or two of them If you decorate the area splendidly, it may lure good luck and fortune to you
203_ItemDescription/5121: A small bonfire that can be placed even on hills In the dark night, together under this light, as long as we are bonded together with the power of friendship, we have nothing to fear Your friend may somehow be on fire, burning down the wall there in the process, but it is all trivial
203_ItemDescription/5122: A big bonfire that can be placed even on hills "Light a torch and deliver this letter," a smart person like you should be capable of following this order without a problem The only issue is that you were trying to teach a goblin to do it for you
203_ItemDescription/5123: A lightsource that make the world so much brighter It can tip over easily so think through where you place them Prepare to have some gold for reparation if you burn down somebody's village Beware of a hero with a feathered cap
203_ItemDescription/5124: A lightsource that make the world so much brighter It can tip over easily so think through where you place them Eventually, somebody will knock over this torch It's not going to be me, and it's not going to happen today Safety inspection is complete, we may now proceed
203_ItemDescription/5125: A portable lantern It won't break even if you throw it, but since it is fueled with bioethanol, you won't be able to make the enemy slip and fall by dispersing it The Game Master must be in relief on the other side of the screen

721_MainMissionDesc/0: The memory orb of "Satyr" protecting the Ruin of Beginning There was the great explosion known as the "Great Destruction" that consumed the land of Craftopia and destroyed all civilizations No one in this land knows the cause of the destruction However, the guardian Satyr protects this land as if they prevent the cause of the destruction from returning to this land
721_MainMissionDesc/1: The memory orb of "Messenger of the Underworld" protecting the Old Garden of Undead Those who survived the Great Destruction sought a shelter from disasters and found the castle The castle was designed to protect people from foreign enemies, but became a prison when that was besieged The warrior who sacrifices themself to protect the people, even after their death, lures the souls of intruders who enter the castle to the underworld
721_MainMissionDesc/2: The memory orb of "Lizard Gunner" protecting the Ruin of Hunters A young lizard from the tribe of hunters abandoned their customs and became fascinated by the modern weapon found in the ruin The inventor of these relics would never thought that these terrifying weapons would be used against human beings
721_MainMissionDesc/3: The memory orb of "Griffin" protecting the Old Garden of Storms A male dragon and a male griffin clashed fiercely in the sky above the grassy meadow The winner got everything in their hands and became the king of the meadow The loser, on the other hand, became the guardian of the narrow sky created by the earth, and has repelled anyone who attempted to break the seal
721_MainMissionDesc/4: The memory orb of "Noble Frog" protecting the Labyrinth of Torrent The former aristocrat who ruled the country was rejected by those who respected their traditions because they loved foreign cultures more than their own culture But, the aristocrat exiles anyone who approaches the seal, even after their own body has been completely transformed They're still doing this, to protect their own people, as if it is their duty to do so
721_MainMissionDesc/5: The memory orb of "Lizard Executioner" protecting the Old Garden of Massacre The executioner has never found condemnation good Justice without fear is powerless The executioner had to swing an axe to maintain the peace, regardless of his own will Fear without justice is evil The executioner must condemn intruders to prevent the nightmarish days from happening again
721_MainMissionDesc/6: The memory orb of "Fenrir" protecting the Ruin of Everfrost After the Great Destruction, the lord of wolves had gone in search of food The white wolf, whose body has been transformed by the blessing of the earth, will wait and block intruders until the return of the lord

999_NoGameText/Handover/Detail:
- บางไอเทมที่โอนย้ายอาจทำงานไม่เหมือน Craftopia ในเวอร์ชั่นเก่า
- โปรดระวังในการลบเอนชานท์จากไอเทมที่ถูกโอนย้ายไปแล้ว, เพราะไม่สามารถนำกลับคืนมาได้
- หากลืมโอนย้ายบางไอเทม สามารถโอนย้ายได้อีกครั้ง
